channel.title: [PI][614] 'HighTivity' Need 2 Partners!
channel.description:
Hello, I started the idea of 'HighTivity'. I bought the domain immediately, and thought of what I was going to do. I figured out I should start a new RSPS, and so I bought webhosting. I installed SMF and made a nice homepage.
What will I be doing?
Paying for the domain + hosting Keeping my old computer in my basement running 24/7 (unless power shuts off, etc.) Coding, a little. Editing the site + forums. Making sure people are following the rules.
What will you be doing?
Advertising Basically coding. I'm not too good at coding thats why I need partners :)
It'll be a 614 spawn server based off of IntDub, Project Insanity.
Pics of source:
[img]http://i.imgur.com/6RI5Y.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/i7koQ.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/NY0Y1.png[/img]
Features:
Torva Korasi Vestas Chaotics Veng Barrage 100% 1v1 Edge PKing Working Jad PK Point shops PK timer Everytime you kill someone you get 5 pk points.
Msn: anthonydukaj@live.com
Hit me up if interested.
Thanks, anthonyduka
